data.name: TRACHEOSTOMY TUBE
data.description:
## COMPOSITION
- 100% PVC and 100% DEHP-FREE PVC and Silicone

## STERILIZATION
- Ethylene Oxide (EO) Sterile

## PRESENTATIONS
- PVC and DEHP-FREE PVC and Silicone
- Encapsulated radiopaque stripe all along the tube length
- Highly Visible Size Indication along the Tubing
- Cuffed and Uncuffed

## PERFORMANCE
- Easy introduction
- Smooth Surface and Tips

## ANESTHASIA
